### ============================================================================
### 3. TRANSCRIPTION MANAGEMENT (READ/DELETE)
### ============================================================================

### 3.1 Get all transcriptions for a specific user
GET {{host}}/transcriptions/user/{{keycloakId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.2 Get details of a single transcription by ID
GET {{host}}/transcriptions/1
Accept: application/json

### 3.3 Delete transcription by ID
DELETE {{host}}/transcriptions/1
Accept: application/json

### 3.4 Get all transcriptions (Admin/Test)
GET {{host}}/test/get-all
Accept: application/json

### 3.5 Download transcription file (PDF)
GET {{host}}/transcriptions/1/download?language=POLISH
Accept: application/pdf